help.addresses__en:
# Addresses

Addresses are some of the most useful information for the map.

Although addresses are often represented as parts of streets, in OpenStreetMap
they're recorded as attributes of buildings and places along streets.

You can add address information to places mapped as building outlines
as well as those mapped as single points. The optimal source of address
data is from an on-the-ground survey or personal knowledge - as with any
other feature, copying from commercial sources like Google Maps is strictly
forbidden.
help.addresses__transl:
# Addrese

Addrese su neke od najkorisnijih informacija na karti.

Iako su adrese često predstavljene kao dijelovi ulica, na karti OpenStreetMap
su one spremljene kao atributi građevina i mjesta uz ulice.

Možete dodati informaciju o adresama mjesta koja su ucrtana kao i vanjske linije građevina takođe
kao i onih koja su ucrtana kao obične tačke. Optimalni izvor podataka adresa
se dobija iz istraživanja na licu mjesta ili ličnim znanjem- kao što je slučaj sam bilo kojom drugom značajkom,
kopiranje iz komercijalnih izvora kao što je Google Maps je striktno
zabranjeno.
help.buildings__en:
# Buildings

OpenStreetMap is the world's largest database of buildings. You can create
and improve this database.

### Selecting

You can select a building by clicking on its border. This will highlight the
building and open a small tools menu and a sidebar showing more information
about the building.

### Modifying

Sometimes buildings are incorrectly placed or have incorrect tags.

To move an entire building, select it, then click the 'Move' tool. Move your
mouse to shift the building, and click when it's correctly placed.

To fix the specific shape of a building, click and drag the nodes that form
its border into better places.

### Creating

One of the main questions around adding buildings to the map is that
OpenStreetMap records buildings both as shapes and points. The rule of thumb
is to _map a building as a shape whenever possible_, and map companies, homes,
amenities, and other things that operate out of buildings as points placed
within the building shape.

Start drawing a building as a shape by clicking the 'Area' button in the top
left of the interface, and end it either by pressing 'Return' on your keyboard
or clicking on the first node drawn to close the shape.

### Deleting

If a building is entirely incorrect - you can see that it doesn't exist in satellite
imagery and ideally have confirmed locally that it's not present - you can delete
it, which removes it from the map. Be cautious when deleting features -
like any other edit, the results are seen by everyone and satellite imagery
is often out of date, so the building could simply be newly built.

You can delete a building by clicking on it to select it, then clicking the
trash can icon or pressing the 'Delete' key.
help.buildings__transl:
# Građevine

OpenStreetMap karta je najveća svjetska baza građevina. Možete napraviti
i proširiti ovu bazu podataka.

### Odabir

Možete odabrati građevinu odnosno zgradu klikom na njene granice. Ovo će označiti
građevinu i otvoriti mali meni alata i bočnu traku koja pokazuje više informacija
o građevinama.

### Izmjena

Ponekad su građevine nepravilno postavljene ili imaju nepravilne oznake.

Da bi pomjerili cijelu građevinu, odaberite je, i onda kliknite na alat 'Pomicanje'. Pomaknite Vaš
miš da pomjerite građevinu, i kliknite kada je ona pravilno postavljena.

Da bi popravili specifičan oblik građevine, kliknite i povucite čvorove koji formiraju
njenu granicu na bolje mjesto.

### Pravljenje

Jedno od glavnih pitanja oko dodavanja zgrada karti je to da
OpenStreetMap snima građevine i kao oblike i kao tačke. Pravilo palca
je _ucrtavati građevinu kao oblik gdje god je moguće_, kao i ucrtavati kompanije, domove,
i druge značajne građevine, a i druge stvari koje operiraju van građevina kao tačke smještene
unutar oblika građevine.

Započnite crtati građevinu kao oblik klikom na dugme 'Područje' u gornjem
lijevom dijelu interfejsa, i završite je pritiskom na 'Backspace' na Vašoj tastaturi
ili klikom na prvi čvor koji je ucrtan kako bi zatvorili oblik.

### Brisanje

Ukoliko je građevina u potpunosti netačna - možete vidjeti da ne postoji u satelitskim
slikama i idealno dobro bi bilo da potvrdite da lokalno nije prisutna -  možete je obrisati,
što je uklanja sa karte. Budite pažljivi kada brišete značajke -
kao i svako drugo uređivanje, rezultate vide svi i satelitske slike
su često stare, tako da bi građevina mogla biti novoizgrađena.

Možete izbrisati građevinu klikom na nju da bi ste je odabrali, i onda kliknuti na
ikonu kante za smeće ili pritiskom na tipku 'Delete'.
help.editing_saving__en:
# Editing & Saving

This editor is designed to work primarily online, and you're accessing
it through a website right now.

### Selecting Features

To select a map feature, like a road or point of interest, click
on it on the map. This will highlight the selected feature, open a panel with
details about it, and show a menu of things you can do with the feature.

To select multiple features, hold down the 'Shift' key. Then either click
on the features you want to select, or drag on the map to draw a rectangle.
This will draw a box and select all the points within it.

### Saving Edits

When you make changes like editing roads, buildings, and places, these are
stored locally until you save them to the server. Don't worry if you make
a mistake - you can undo changes by clicking the undo button, and redo
changes by clicking the redo button.

Click 'Save' to finish a group of edits - for instance, if you've completed
an area of town and would like to start on a new area. You'll have a chance
to review what you've done, and the editor supplies helpful suggestions
and warnings if something doesn't seem right about the changes.

If everything looks good, you can enter a short comment explaining the change
you made, and click 'Save' again to post the changes
to [OpenStreetMap.org](http://www.openstreetmap.org/), where they are visible
to all other users and available for others to build and improve upon.

If you can't finish your edits in one sitting, you can leave the editor
window and come back (on the same browser and computer), and the
editor application will offer to restore your work.
help.editing_saving__transl:
# Uređivanje i spremanje

Ovaj editor je dizajniran da primarno radi online, i pristupate mu
kroz web stranicu upravo sada.

### Odabir značajki

Da odaberete značajku na karti, kao npr. cestu ili tačku od interesa, kliknite
na istu na karti. Ovo će osvijetliti odabranu značajku, otvoriti panel sa
detaljima o istoj, i pokazati izbor stvari koje možete uraditi sa značajkom.

Da odaberete više značajki odjednom, držite tipku 'Shift'. Onda ili kliknite
na značajke koje želite odabrati, ili povucite na karti da nacrtate pravougaonik.
Ovo će nacrtati kutiju i odabrati sve tačke unutar iste.

### Spremanje uređivanja

Kada uradite promjene kao što su uređivanje cesta, zgrada i mjesta, isti se
pohranjuju lokalno sve dok ih ne spremite na server. Ne brinite ako napravite
grešku - možete poništiti promjene klikom na dugme "Poništiti", i vratiti
promjene klikom na dugme "Vratiti".

Kliknite na 'Spremiti' da završite grupu uređivanja - npr, ako ste završili
dio grada i želite započeti uređivanje na novom području. Imaćete priliku
da pregledate šta ste uradili, a editor daje prijedloge od pomoći
i upozorenja ako se nešto ne čini uredu sa promjenama.

Ako sve izgleda uredno, možete unijeti kratak komentar kojim objašnjavate promjene
koje ste napravili, i kliknite na 'Spremiti' opet kako bi postavili promjene
na [OpenStreetMap.org](http://www.openstreetmap.org/), gdje su one vidljive
svim drugim korisnicima i dostupne za druge da ih dalje uređuju i poboljšavaju.

Ako ne možete završiti vaša uređivanja u jednom sjedenju, možete napustiti prozor
editora i vratiti se (na istom pregledniku i računaru), i
aplikacija editora će ponuditi da vratite vaš rad.
help.gps__en:
# GPS

GPS data is the most trusted source of data for OpenStreetMap. This editor
supports local traces - `.gpx` files on your local computer. You can collect
this kind of GPS trace with a number of smartphone applications as well as
personal GPS hardware.

For information on how to perform a GPS survey, read
[Surveying with a GPS](http://learnosm.org/en/beginner/using-gps/).

To use a GPX track for mapping, drag and drop the GPX file onto the map
editor. If it's recognized, it will be added to the map as a bright purple
line. Click on the 'Map Data' menu on the right side to enable,
disable, or zoom to this new GPX-powered layer.

The GPX track isn't directly uploaded to OpenStreetMap - the best way to
use it is to draw on the map, using it as a guide for the new features that
you add, and also to [upload it to OpenStreetMap](http://www.openstreetmap.org/trace/create)
for other users to use.
help.help__en:
# Help

This is an editor for [OpenStreetMap](http://www.openstreetmap.org/), the
free and editable map of the world. You can use it to add and update
data in your area, making an open-source and open-data map of the world
better for everyone.

Edits that you make on this map will be visible to everyone who uses
OpenStreetMap. In order to make an edit, you'll need a
[free OpenStreetMap account](https://www.openstreetmap.org/user/new).

The [iD editor](http://ideditor.com/) is a collaborative project with [source
code available on GitHub](https://github.com/openstreetmap/iD).
help.imagery__en:
# Imagery

Aerial imagery is an important resource for mapping. A combination of
airplane flyovers, satellite views, and freely-compiled sources are available
in the editor under the 'Background Settings' menu on the right.

By default a [Bing Maps](http://www.bing.com/maps/) satellite layer is
presented in the editor, but as you pan and zoom the map to new geographical
areas, new sources will become available. Some countries, like the United
States, France, and Denmark have very high-quality imagery available for some areas.

Imagery is sometimes offset from the map data because of a mistake on the
imagery provider's side. If you see a lot of roads shifted from the background,
don't immediately move them all to match the background. Instead you can adjust
the imagery so that it matches the existing data by clicking 'Fix alignment' at
the bottom of the Background Settings UI.
help.imagery__transl:
# Satelitske slike

Satelitske slike su važan resurs za mapiranje. Kombinacija
preleta avionom, satelitski pogledi i slobodno sastavljeni izvorisu dostupni
u uređivaču pod menijem 'Podešavanja pozadine' na desnoj strani.

U početnik postavkama satelitski sloj [Bing Maps] (http://www.bing.com/maps/) je
prezentiran u uređivaču, ali kako pomičete i uvećavate kartu na nova geografska
područja, novi će izvori postati dostupni. Neke zemlje, poput Sjedinjenih
Država, Francuske i Danske imaju slike vrlo visoke kvalitete na raspolaganju za neka područja.

Satelitske slike ponekad odstupaju od podataka karte, zbog greške na
strani davatelja satelitskih slika. Ako vidite puno cesta pomjerenih u pozadini.
nemojte ih odmah sve premještati kako bi se slagale sa pozadinom. Umjesto toga možete podesiti
satelitske slike tako da odgovaraju postojećim podacima klikom na 'Popravljanje poravnanja', na
dnu interfejsa Podešavanja pozadine.
help.inspector__en:
# Using the Inspector

The inspector is the section on the left side of the page that allows you to
edit the details of the selected feature.

### Selecting a Feature Type

After you add a point, line, or area, you can choose what type of feature it
is, like whether it's a highway or residential road, supermarket or cafe.
The inspector will display buttons for common feature types, and you can
find others by typing what you're looking for in the search box.

Click the 'i' in the bottom-right-hand corner of a feature type button to
learn more about it. Click a button to choose that type.

### Using Forms and Editing Tags

After you choose a feature type, or when you select a feature that already
has a type assigned, the inspector will display fields with details about
the feature like its name and address.

Below the fields you see, you can click icons to add other details,
like [Wikipedia](http://www.wikipedia.org/) information, wheelchair
access, and more.

At the bottom of the inspector, click 'Additional tags' to add arbitrary
other tags to the element. [Taginfo](http://taginfo.openstreetmap.org/) is a
great resource for learn more about popular tag combinations.

Changes you make in the inspector are automatically applied to the map.
You can undo them at any time by clicking the 'Undo' button.
help.inspector__transl:
# Korištenje inspektora

Inspektor je element korisničkog interfejsa na lijevoj strani
stranice koji vam dozvoljava da uređujete odabranu značajku.

### Odabir vrste značajke

Nakon što dodate tačku, liniju ili područje, možete birati koja je to vrsta značajke,
kao npr. da li je to cesta ili rezidencijalna cesta, supermarket ili kafe.
Inspector će prikazati dugmad za vrste općih značajki, i možete
naći druge unošenjem onoga što tražite u polje za pretragu.

Kliknite na 'i' u donjem desnom uglu dugmeta vrste značajke da
saznate više o istoj. Kliknite na dugme da odaberete tu vrstu.

### Korištenje obrazaca i oznaka za uređivanje

Nakon što odaberete vrstu značajke, ili kada odaberete značajku koja već
ima pripisanu vrstu, inspektor će prikazati polja sa detaljima o
značajki kao što je njen naziv i adresa.

Ispod polja koje vidite, možete kliknuti na ikone da dodate druge detalje,
kao što su informacije sa stranice [Wikipedia](http://www.wikipedia.org/), pristup
za invalidska kolica, i više.

Na dnu inspektora, kliknite 'Dodatne oznake' da dodate još neke
druge oznake elementu. [Taginfo](http://taginfo.openstreetmap.org/) je
odličan izvor za više informacija o popularnim kombinacijama oznaka.

Promjene koje napravite u inspektoru bivaju automatski primijenjene na karti.
Možete ih poništiti bilo kad klikom na dugme za poništavanje.
help.relations__en:
# Relations

A relation is a special type of feature in OpenStreetMap that groups together
other features. For example, two common types of relations are *route relations*,
which group together sections of road that belong to a specific freeway or
highway, and *multipolygons*, which group together several lines that define
a complex area (one with several pieces or holes in it like a donut).

The group of features in a relation are called *members*. In the sidebar, you can
see which relations a feature is a member of, and click on a relation there
to select the it. When the relation is selected, you can see all of its
members listed in the sidebar and highlighted on the map.

For the most part, iD will take care of maintaining relations automatically
while you edit. The main thing you should be aware of is that if you delete a
section of road to redraw it more accurately, you should make sure that the
new section is a member of the same relations as the original.

## Editing Relations

If you want to edit relations, here are the basics.

To add a feature to a relation, select the feature, click the "+" button in the
"All relations" section of the sidebar, and select or type the name of the relation.

To create a new relation, select the first feature that should be a member,
click the "+" button in the "All relations" section, and select "New relation...".

To remove a feature from a relation, select the feature and click the trash
button next to the relation you want to remove it from.

You can create multipolygons with holes using the "Merge" tool. Draw two areas (inner
and outer), hold the Shift key and click on each of them to select them both, and then
click the "Merge" (+) button.
help.relations__transl:
# Relacije

Relacija je posebna vrsta značajke OpenStreetMap projektu koja grupira
druge značajke. Na primjer, dvije uobičajene vrste relacija su *relacije ruta*,
koje zajedno grupiraju dijelove puta koji pripadaju posebnom putu ili
autoputu, i  *multipoligoni*, koji zajedno grupiraju nekoliko linija koje definiraju
složeno područje (jedno sa više dijelova ili rupa u sebi kao krofna).

Grupa značajki u relaciji se naziva *članovi*. Na Bočnoj traic, možete
vidjeti kojoj relaciji pripada član, i kliknuti na relaciju
da je odaberete. Kada je relacija odabrana možete vidjeti sve njene
članove izlistane na bočnoj traci i osvijetljene na karti.

U većini slučajeva, iD editor će voditi računa o održavanju relacija automatski
dok uređujete. Glavna stvar koje trebate biti svjesni jeste da ako izbrišete
dio puta u namjeri da ga nacrtate tačnije, morate biti sigurni da je
novi dio član istih relacija kao i original.

## Uređivanje relacija

Ako želite uređivati relacije, ovo su osnove.

Da dodate značajku relaciji, odaberite značajku, kliknite na dugme "+" u
dijelu "Sve relacije" na bočnoj traci, i izaberite ili ukucajte naziv relacije.

Da napravite novu relaciju, prvo odaberite značajku koja treba biti član,
kliknite na dugme "+" u dijelu "Sve relacije", i izaberite "Nova relacija...".

Da uklonite značajku iz relacije, odaberite značajku i kliknite na dugme smeće
koje se pojavljuje uy relaciju iz koje je želite ukloniti.

Možete praviti multipoligone sa rupama koristeći alat "Spojiti". Nacrtajte dva područja (unutrašnje i
vanjsko), držite tipku Shift i kliknite na svaku od njih da ih izaberete, a potom
kliknite na dugme "Spojiti" (+).
help.roads__en:
# Roads

You can create, fix, and delete roads with this editor. Roads can be all
kinds: paths, highways, trails, cycleways, and more - any often-crossed
segment should be mappable.

### Selecting

Click on a road to select it. An outline should become visible, along
with a small tools menu on the map and a sidebar showing more information
about the road.

### Modifying

Often you'll see roads that aren't aligned to the imagery behind them
or to a GPS track. You can adjust these roads so they are in the correct
place.

First click on the road you want to change. This will highlight it and show
control points along it that you can drag to better locations. If
you want to add new control points for more detail, double-click a part
of the road without a node, and one will be added.

If the road connects to another road, but doesn't properly connect on
the map, you can drag one of its control points onto the other road in
order to join them. Having roads connect is important for the map
and essential for providing driving directions.

You can also click the 'Move' tool or press the `M` shortcut key to move the entire road at
one time, and then click again to save that movement.

### Deleting

If a road is entirely incorrect - you can see that it doesn't exist in satellite
imagery and ideally have confirmed locally that it's not present - you can delete
it, which removes it from the map. Be cautious when deleting features -
like any other edit, the results are seen by everyone and satellite imagery
is often out of date, so the road could simply be newly built.

You can delete a road by clicking on it to select it, then clicking the
trash can icon or pressing the 'Delete' key.

### Creating

Found somewhere there should be a road but there isn't? Click the 'Line'
icon in the top-left of the editor or press the shortcut key `2` to start drawing
a line.

Click on the start of the road on the map to start drawing. If the road
branches off from an existing road, start by clicking on the place where they connect.

Then click on points along the road so that it follows the right path, according
to satellite imagery or GPS. If the road you are drawing crosses another road, connect
it by clicking on the intersection point. When you're done drawing, double-click
or press 'Return' or 'Enter' on your keyboard.
help.roads__transl:
# Putevi

Možete crtati, popravljati, i brisati puteve sa ovim uređivačem. Putevi mogu biti svih
vrsta: staze, ceste, tragovi, biciklističke staze, i više - bilo koji često prelaženi
segment bi trebao biti moguć za ucrtavanje.

### Odabir

Kliknite na put da ga odaberete. vanjska linija bi trebala postati vidljiva, zajedno
sa malim menijem alata na karti i bočnom trakom koja pokazuje više informacija
o putu.

### Izmjena

Često ćete vidjeti puteve koji nisu poravnati da satelistskim slikama iza njih
ili sa GPS trasom. Možete podesiti ove puteve tako da su na pravom
mjestu.

Prvi klik na put koji želite mijenjati. Ovo će ga označiti i pokazati
kontrolne tačke uz njega koje možete pomjerati na bolje lokacije. Ukoliko
želite dodati nove kontrolne tačke za više detalja, dva puta kliknite na dio
puta bez čvora, i jedan će biti dodan.

Ukoliko se put povezuje na drugi put, ali se neprikladno povezuje na
kartu, možete povući jednu od njegovih kontnrolnih tačaka na drugi put u
namjeri da ih spojite. Održavanje puteva povezanim je važno za kartu
i od vitalnoj je značaja za obezbjeđivanje uputa za vožnju.

Možete takođe kliknuti na alat 'Pomjeriti' ili pritisnuti 'M' tipku koja je prečica da pomičete cijeli put
istovremeno, i onda kliknete opet da spasite to pomicanje. 

### Brisanje

Ukoliko je put u potpunosti netačan - možete vidjeti da ne postoji na satelitskoj
slici i idealno bi bilo da potvrdite da nije prisutan lokalno - možete ga izbrisati,
što ga uklanja sa karte. Budite pažljivi kada brišete značajke -
kao i svako drugo uređivanje, rezultati su vidljivi svima i satelitske slike
su često stare, tako da bi put mogao ustvari biti novoizgrađeni.

Možete izbrisati put klikom na njega da ga odaberete, i onda klikajući na
ikonu kante za smeće ili pritiskom na tipku 'Delete'.

### Pravljenje

Našli ste negdje da bi tu trebao biti put ali ga nema? Kliknite ikonu 'Linija'
u donjem lijevom uglu uređivača ili pritisnite tipku`2` da bi započeli crtanje
linije.

Kliknite na početak puta na kartu da započnete crtanje. Ukoliko se put
granan sa postojećeg puta, započnite sa mjesta gdje se povezuju.

Onda kliknite na tačke uzduž puta tako da slijedi pravu putanju, prema
satelitskim slikama ili prema GPS-u. Ukoliko se put koji crtate križa sa drugim putem, povežite
ga klikom na tačku križanja. Kada završite crtanje, dva puta kliknite
ili pritisnite 'Backspace' ili 'Enter' na Vašoj tastaturi.

inspector.no_documentation_combination__en: There is no documentation available for this tag combination
inspector.no_documentation_combination__transl: Nema dostupne dokumentacije za ovu kombinaciju oznaka
inspector.no_documentation_key__en: There is no documentation available for this key
inspector.no_documentation_key__transl: Nema dostupne dokumentacije za ovaj ključ

areas.add__en: Areas are used to show the boundaries of features like lakes, buildings, and residential areas. They can be also be used for more detailed mapping of many features you might normally map as points. **Click the Area button to add a new area.**
areas.corner__en: Areas are drawn by placing nodes that mark the boundary of the area. **Place the starting node on one of the corners of the playground.**
areas.corner__transl: Područja se crtaju postavljanjem čvorova koji označavaju granicu područja. **Postavite početni čvor na uglovima igrališta.**
areas.describe__en: **Add a name, and close the feature editor**
areas.place__en: Draw the area by placing more nodes. Finish the area by clicking on the starting node. **Draw an area for the playground.**
areas.place__transl: Nacrtati područje postavljanjem više čvorova. Završiti područje klikom na početni čvor. **Nacrtati područje za igralište.**

lines.add__en: Lines are used to represent features such as roads, railroads and rivers. **Click the Line button to add a new line.**
lines.add__transl: Linije se koriste da predstave značajke kao što su putevi, željezničke pruge i rijeke. **Kliknite na dugme 'Linija' da dodate novu liniju.**
lines.describe__en: **Name the road and close the feature editor.**
lines.describe__transl: **Dajte naziv cesti i zatvorite uređivač značajki.**
lines.finish__en: Lines can be finished by clicking on the last node again. **Finish drawing the road.**
lines.finish__transl: Linije mogu biti završene ponovnim klikom na posljednji čvor. **Završite crtanje ceste.**
lines.intersect__en: Click to add more nodes to the line. You can drag the map while drawing if necessary. Roads, and many other types of lines, are part of a larger network. It is important for these lines to be connected properly in order for routing applications to work. **Click on Flower Street, to create an intersection connecting the two lines.**
lines.intersect__transl: Kliknite da dodate više čvorova liniji. Možete povlačiti kartu dok crtate ukoliko je potrebno. Putevi, i mnogo drugih vrsta linija su dio veće mreže. Važno je da se ove linije povežu pravilno da bi aplikacije za routing radile.  **Kliknite na neku ulicu da napravite presjek koji povezuje dvije linije.**
lines.residential__en: There are different types of roads, the most common of which is Residential. **Choose the Residential road type**
lines.residential__transl: Postoje različite vrste puteva, od kojih su najčešće rezidencijalne ceste. **Odaberite vrstu 'rezidencijalna cesta'**
lines.restart__en: The road needs to intersect Flower Street.
lines.restart__transl: Put treba da se križa sa ulicom 'Flower Street'.
lines.start__en: **Start the line by clicking on the end of the road.**
lines.wrong_preset__en: You didn't select the Residential road type. **Click here to choose again**
lines.wrong_preset__transl: Niste odabrali rezidencijalnu vrstu ceste. **Kliknite ovdje da opet odaberete**

navigation.drag__en: The main map area shows OpenStreetMap data on top of a background. You can navigate by dragging and scrolling, just like any web map. **Drag the map!**
navigation.drag__transl: Glavno područje karte pokazuje podatke karte OpenStreetMap iznad pozadine. Možete upravljati povlačenjem i skrolanjem kao u bilo kojoj drugoj web aplikaciji. **Povuci kartu!**
navigation.header__en: The header shows us the feature type.
navigation.pane__en: When a feature is selected, the feature editor is displayed. The header shows us the feature type and the main pane shows the feature's attributes, such as its name and address. **Close the feature editor with the close button in the top right.**
navigation.pane__transl: Kada je značajka odabrana, uređivač značajki biva prikazan. Zaglavlje nam pokazuje vrstu značajke i glavni panel nam pokazuje osobine značajke, kao što su njen naziv i adresa. **Zatvorite uređivač značajki sa dugmetom za zatvaranje koje se nalazi u gornjem desnom uglu.**
navigation.select__en: Map features are represented three ways: using points, lines or areas. All features can be selected by clicking on them. **Click on the point to select it.**
navigation.select__transl: Značajke karte su predstavljene na tri načina: korištenjem tačaka, linija ili područja. Sve značajke mogu biti odabrane klikom na iste. **Kliknite na tačku da je odaberete.**

points.add__en: Points can be used to represent features such as shops, restaurants and monuments. They mark a specific location, and describe what's there. **Click the Point button to add a new point.**
points.add__transl: Tačke mogu biti korištene da predstave značajke kao što su prodavnice, restorani i spomenici. One označavaju specifičnu lokaciu i opisuju šta je tamo.  **Kliknite na dugme 'Tačka' da dodate novu tačku.**
points.close__en: The feature editor can be closed by clicking on the close button. **Close the feature editor**
points.close__transl: Uređivač značajki može biti zatvoren klikom na dugme za zatvaranje. **zatvorite uređivač značajki**
points.delete__en: The menu around the point contains operations that can be performed on it, including delete. **Delete the point.**
points.delete__transl: meni oko tačke sadrži operacije koje mogu biti izvršene na istoj, uključujući brisanje. **Obrisati tačku.**
points.describe__en: The point is now marked as a cafe. Using the feature editor, we can add more information about the feature. **Add a name**
points.describe__transl: Ova tačka je sada označena kao kafe. Korištenjem uređivača značajki, možemo dodati više informacija o značajki. **Dodati naziv**
points.fixname__en: **Change the name and close the feature editor.**
points.place__en: The point can be placed by clicking on the map. **Place the point on top of the building.**
points.place__transl: Tačka može biti postavljena klikom na kartu. **Postavite tačku na vrh građevine.**
points.reselect__en: Often points will already exist, but have mistakes or be incomplete. We can edit existing points. **Select the point you just created.**
points.reselect__transl: Često će tačke već postojati, ali će imati greške ili neće biti kompletne. Možemo uređivati postojeće tačke. **Odaberite tačku koju ste upravo napravili.**
points.reselect_delete__en: All features on the map can be deleted. **Click on the point you created.**
points.reselect_delete__transl: Sve značajke na karti mogu biti izbrisane. **Kliknite na tačku koju ste napravili.**
points.search__en: There are many different features that can be represented by points. The point you just added is a Cafe. **Search for '{name}'**
points.search__transl: Postoji mnogo različitih značajki koje mogu biti predstavljene tačkama. Tačka koju ste upravo dodali je kafe. **Tražiti '{name}' **

startediting.help__en: More documentation and this walkthrough are available here.
startediting.help__transl: Više dokumentacije i ovo uputstvo su dostupni ovdje.
startediting.save__en: Don't forget to regularly save your changes!
startediting.save__transl: Ne zaboravite da često spašavate Vaše promjene!

map_data.autohidden__en: These features have been automatically hidden because too many would be shown on the screen.  You can zoom in to edit them.

add_area.description__en: Add parks, buildings, lakes or other areas to the map.
add_area.description__transl: Dodajte karti parkove, zgrade, jezera ili druga područja.
add_area.tail__en: Click on the map to start drawing an area, like a park, lake, or building.
add_area.tail__transl: Kliknite na kartu da bi ste počeli crtati područje, kao što je park, jezero ili zgrada.

add_line.description__en: Add highways, streets, pedestrian paths, canals or other lines to the map.
add_line.description__transl: Dodajte puteve, ulice, pješačke staze, kanale ili druge linije na kartu.
add_line.tail__en: Click on the map to start drawing a road, path, or route.
add_line.tail__transl: Kliknite na kartu da počnete crtati cestu, stazu ili rutu.

add_point.description__en: Add restaurants, monuments, postal boxes or other points to the map.
add_point.description__transl: Dodajte restorane, spomenike, poštanske urede ili druge tačke na kartu.
add_point.tail__en: Click on the map to add a point.
add_point.tail__transl: Kliknite na kartu da počnete crtati cestu, stazu ili rutu.

draw_area.tail__en: Click to add nodes to your area. Click the first node to finish the area.
draw_area.tail__transl: Kliknite da dodate čvorove Vašem području. Kliknite na prvi čvor da završite područje.

draw_line.tail__en: Click to add more nodes to the line. Click on other lines to connect to them, and double-click to end the line.
draw_line.tail__transl: Kliknite da dodate više čvorova liniji. Kliknite na druge linije da bi ste ih povezali, i dva puta kliknite na kraj linije.

annotation.vertex__en: Added a node to a way.

add_member.annotation__en: Added a member to a relation.

change_role.annotation__en: Changed the role of a relation member.

circularize.connected_to_hidden__en: This can't be made circular because it is connected to a hidden feature.
circularize.not_closed__en: This can't be made circular because it's not a loop.
circularize.not_closed__transl: Ovo se ne može napraviti kružnim jer to nije petlja.
circularize.too_large__en: This can't be made circular because not enough of it is currently visible.

annotation.area__en: Connected a way to an area.
annotation.line__en: Connected a way to a line.
annotation.point__en: Connected a way to a point.

continue.multiple__en: Several lines can be continued here. To choose a line, press the Shift key and click on it to select it.
continue.multiple__transl: Ovdje nekoliko linija mogu biti nastavljene. Da odaberete liniju, pritisnite tipku "Shift" i kliknite na nju za odabir.
continue.not_eligible__en: No line can be continued here.
continue.not_eligible__transl: Ovdje nijedna linija ne može biti nastavljena

annotation.vertex__en: Deleted a node from a way.

delete.connected_to_hidden__en: This can't be deleted because it is connected to a hidden feature.
delete.incomplete_relation__en: This feature can't be deleted because it hasn't been fully downloaded.
delete.incomplete_relation__transl: Ova značajka se ne može izbrisati zato što nije u cijelosti preuzeta.

delete_member.annotation__en: Removed a member from a relation.

disconnect.connected_to_hidden__en: This can't be disconnected because it is connected to a hidden feature.
disconnect.description__en: Disconnect these lines/areas from each other.
disconnect.description__transl: Razdvojite ove linije/ područja jedne od drugih.
disconnect.not_connected__en: There aren't enough lines/areas here to disconnect.
disconnect.not_connected__transl: Ne postoji dovoljno linija/ područja da bi se prekinula veza.

merge.incomplete_relation__en: These features can't be merged because at least one hasn't been fully downloaded.
merge.not_adjacent__en: These lines can't be merged because they aren't connected.
merge.not_adjacent__transl: Ove linije ne mogu biti spojene u jednu zato što nisu povezane.
merge.not_eligible__transl: Ove značajke ne mogu biti spojene.
merge.restriction__en: These lines can't be merged because at least one is a member of a "{relation}" relation.
merge.restriction__transl: Ove linije ne mogu biti spojene u jednu zato što je bar jedna član "{relation}" relacije.

annotation.vertex__en: Moved a node in a way.

move.connected_to_hidden__en: This can't be moved because it is connected to a hidden feature.
move.description__en: Move this to a different location.
move.incomplete_relation__en: This feature can't be moved because it hasn't been fully downloaded.
move.incomplete_relation__transl: Ova značajka se ne može pomaknuti zato što nije u cijelosti preuzeta.
move.too_large__en: This can't be moved because not enough of it is currently visible.

annotation.area__en: Squared the corners of an area.
annotation.line__en: Squared the corners of a line.

orthogonalize.connected_to_hidden__en: This can't be made square because it is connected to a hidden feature.

description.area__en: Square the corners of this area.
description.area__transl: Oblikovati uglove ovo područje u kvadrat.
description.line__en: Square the corners of this line.
description.line__transl: Oblikovati uglove ove linije u kvadrat.

orthogonalize.not_squarish__en: This can't be made square because it is not squarish.
orthogonalize.not_squarish__transl: Ovo se ne može napraviti kvadratom jer nema kvadratnu formu.
orthogonalize.too_large__en: This can't be made square because not enough of it is currently visible.

reverse.description__en: Make this line go in the opposite direction.

rotate.too_large__en: This can't be rotated because not enough of it is currently visible.

split.connected_to_hidden__en: This can't be split because it is connected to a hidden feature.

description.area__en: Split the boundary of this area into two.
description.area__transl: Podijelite granicu ovog područja na dva dijela.
description.line__en: Split this line into two at this node.
description.line__transl: Podijelite ovu liniju na dva dijela na ovom čvoru.
description.multiple__en: Split the lines/area boundaries at this node into two.
description.multiple__transl: Podijelite linije/ područje na dva dijela na ovom čvoru.

split.multiple_ways__en: There are too many lines here to split.
split.multiple_ways__transl: Ovdje postoji previše linija za razdvajanje.
split.not_eligible__en: Lines can't be split at their beginning or end.
split.not_eligible__transl: Linije ne mogu biti razdvojene na njihovom početku i kraju.

straighten.connected_to_hidden__en: This line can't be straightened because it is connected to a hidden feature.
straighten.too_bendy__en: This can't be straightened because it bends too much.
straighten.too_bendy__transl: Ovo ne može biti ispralvjeno jer se previše savija.

restore.description__en: Do you wish to restore unsaved changes from a previous editing session?
restore.description__transl: Želite li vratiti nespremljene promjene od prethodnog uređivanja?

save.error__en: An error occurred while trying to save
save.error__transl: Dogodila se greška prilikom pokušaja spašavanja.
save.help__en: Save changes to OpenStreetMap, making them visible to other users.
save.help__transl: Sačuvajte promjene na OpenStreetMap karti, čineći ih vidljivim drugim korisnicima.
save.unknown_error_details__en: Please ensure you are connected to the internet.

source_switch.lose_changes__en: You have unsaved changes. Switching the map server will discard them. Are you sure you want to switch servers?
source_switch.lose_changes__transl: Imate nespremljenih promjena. Mijenjanje servera karte će ih odbaciti. Sigurni ste da želite promijeniti servere?

splash.text__en: iD is a friendly but powerful tool for contributing to the world's best free world map. This is version {version}. For more information see {website} and report bugs at {github}.
splash.text__transl: ID je prijateljski ali moćan alat za doprinos najboljoj svjetskoj besplatnoj karti svijeta. Ovo je verzija {version}. Za više informacija pogledajte stranicu {website} i prijavite greške na stranici {github}.
splash.welcome__en: Welcome to the iD OpenStreetMap editor

status.offline__en: The API is offline. Please try editing later.
status.offline__transl: API nije na mreži. Molimo pokušajte uređivati kasnije.
status.readonly__en: The API is read-only. You will need to wait to save your changes.
status.readonly__transl: API je samo za čitanje. Moraćete sačekati da sačuvate Vaše promjene.

success.help_html__en: Your changes should appear in the "Standard" layer in a few minutes. Other layers, and certain features, may take longer (details).
success.help_html__transl: Promjene koje ste napravili bi se trebale pojaviti u "standardnom" sloju za nekoliko minuta. Za druge slojeve, i određene značajke, možda bude trebalo duže. (detalji).

validations.many_deletions__en: You're deleting {n} objects. Are you sure you want to do this? This will delete them from the map that everyone else sees on openstreetmap.org.
validations.many_deletions__transl: Broj objekata koje brišete: {n}. Sigurni ste da to želite uraditi? Ovo će iste izbrisati sa karte koju svako drugi vidi na adresi openstreetmap.org.
validations.tag_suggests_area__en: The tag {tag} suggests line should be area, but it is not an area
validations.tag_suggests_area__transl: Oznaka {tag} ukazuje da bi linija trebala biti područje, ali nije područje
validations.untagged_area_tooltip__en: Select a feature type that describes what this area is.
validations.untagged_line_tooltip__en: Select a feature type that describes what this line is.
validations.untagged_point_tooltip__en: Select a feature type that describes what this point is.
